Jenkins demo:

build a dockerized jenkins server
Talk about dockerized jenkins slave infrastructure (for npm vs ruby vs java build envs)
using tagged instances of slaves, different versions of python/ruby supporting libraries
Build environments can be whatever you want only have what is necessary for that specific build, and cleanup afterwards
more efficient use of resources. Wide variety of slvae configurations on a small number of machines. 
Test upgrades of deployments, plugins, deps, can move the actual workspace and run it and roll back if failure 


App deployment demo: 

Create a new container with app server on it
make a change to the app
do an a/b deploy
with linked docker container
Show volume export of mongo container? 

